<h2>Assessments</h2>
<p>Regular assessments fund the maintenance, insurance, and operation of the community's common elements. Assessment amounts, due dates, and payment options are set out in the governing documents and the Board-adopted Assessment Collection Policy, which is contained in the recorded <a href="/reading/03-coa-community-manual/">Community Manual</a>. Questions about your account should go to <a href="mailto:{{ site.email.treasurer }}">{{ site.email.treasurer }}</a> or <a href="mailto:{{ site.email.support }}">{{ site.email.support }}</a>.</p>

<div class="callout">
  <p style="margin:0"><span class="k">What is not posted here.</span> Individual owner ledgers, delinquency and collections information, bank details, and detailed working financials are confidential. Owners may request permitted financial records through the <a href="/forms/">records request option</a>.</p>
